{"tid":1264192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［可心淡不能心死］嗌過不撤不散嘅香港人，我邀請你入嚟補補血！","createTime":"2019-06-28T14:39:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T03:27:46.000Z","uid":70403,"like":133,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f55bb316d498ea77702fa10285ee9cfa47cb0cbe","tid":1264192,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:39:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你有冇嗌過不撤不散？<br />\n你有冇嗌過釋放義士？<br />\n你有冇嗌過撤回暴動定性？<br />\n你有冇企過出嚟食催淚彈？<br />\n你有冇幫過手搬物資？<br />\n有冇一剎那覺得香港人好可愛團結？<br />\n你見到612黑警暴力行為，有冇嬲？<br />\n你見到香港有義士犧牲，有冇喊？<br />\n政府咁無賴，你有冇想反抗？</span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲記唔記得依個四眼仔？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSpYPs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSpYPs.gif&h=88b0fdfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲記唔記得啲物資手勢？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ve3ODE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ve3ODE.png&h=2676b1b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如果你記得或者有做過以上仼何一樣嘢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請你諗下當初點解會出嚟</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好簡單，就係想香港好</span></span></div><br />\n<strong>所以我希望各位香港人，連登仔要keep住團火，團火就熄就望下黑警啲暴力片段，姨姨伯伯顧學生嘅感人片段之類。唔好灰心，唔好氣餒。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">抗爭永遠都係辛苦，唔係一夜間成功</span></div></strong><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">其實香港人已經好撚叻，單單一個月就有遊行200萬人又外國報章又國際法庭關注又全港大和解。<br />\n孫中山都要十次革命啦，所以香港人唔洗心灰意冷。</div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人，抖足精神<br />\n集中七一活動，各花齊放<br />\n七一回歸一齊同政府拜年</span></span></div><br />\n<strong>[size=4]香港人，加油！/size=4]</strong>"},{"pid":"820da3f993961f1758c926ac438fcbb7851d7fbc","tid":1264192,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:41:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">七一係咪會見到高官升旗？想祝賀佢地</span>"},{"pid":"8d68c1bf3a324f5d7fb2aef5e66894226530dba0","tid":1264192,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:42:38.000Z","msg":"最後一推"},{"pid":"fdb10e81186b76797b4e45bee27a93912048c539","tid":1264192,"uid":23895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"加油！"},{"pid":"62f3c4adf487b5e8a8cb57820e45ec735512227c","tid":1264192,"uid":263730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:53:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"846c08049ce84d377108de4c1179c13d24b812c8","tid":1264192,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8aed321563ea98d105328601e7a85c1f9eeaf92e","tid":1264192,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"62f3c4adf487b5e8a8cb57820e45ec735512227c","tid":1264192,"uid":263730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:53:38.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:55:57.000Z","msg":"好攰啊"},{"pid":"21a87c9b425d8ec792d5a20e74199c8e62a8f12b","tid":1264192,"uid":117886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"屌那星 頂硬上呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f197e1f94858777adb683f85b4a814523a01223c","tid":1264192,"uid":194399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T14:59:50.000Z","msg":"抗爭手語,I GET IT . KEEP GOING ,HONGKONGER"},{"pid":"c6cc53d6690bcb71e4ff0ff7622dd278cbc83a27","tid":1264192,"uid":70403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T15:00:23.000Z","msg":"講真點會唔灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己屋企搞成咁。ig，fb少咗好多文宣<br />\n所以上嚟連登打下文抒發下感受<im